55
00:07:18,270 --> 00:07:18,830
Serve tea.

56
00:07:20,330 --> 00:07:22,740
[Black bees]

57
00:07:30,270 --> 00:07:30,920
Miss Zhu,

58
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:33,200
this painting is “Bai Ze's Supernatural Creatures”

59
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:35,000
painted by Bai Ze that year.

60
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:36,510
500 years ago,

61
00:07:36,950 --> 00:07:38,480
this painting was given by Monk Lotus

62
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,760
to my ancestor

63
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,200
and passed on from generation to generation.

64
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:44,390
Do you mean

65
00:07:45,510 --> 00:07:46,720
this is from Monk Lotus?

66
00:07:47,670 --> 00:07:48,110
Yeah.

67
00:07:49,350 --> 00:07:51,670
My ancestor and Monk Lotus were confidants.

68
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:54,110
This painting has been placed in my mansion.

69
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:57,670
But a change has taken place

70
00:07:58,070 --> 00:07:59,160
