71
00:07:59,160 --> 00:07:59,950
What change?

72
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,040
If beasts touch it,

73
00:08:04,110 --> 00:08:05,320
it will emit fluorescence.

74
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,440
You should know

75
00:08:09,790 --> 00:08:12,000
my son often looks after beasts secretly

76
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,550
in the house.

77
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:16,600
Unintentionally,.

78
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,440
I discovered the mystery of this painting.

79
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:21,270
This painting is unique in its style.

80
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,790
I didn't expect it to be so mysterious.

81
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:27,790
Now that Monk Lotus has given it to your ancestor,

82
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:31,390
