83
00:08:35,710 --> 00:08:37,910
I know you and Monk Lotus

84
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,880
are friends.

85
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:41,000
It's the most suitable

86
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,280
to let you keep this painting.

87
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:44,640
Well,

88
00:08:46,110 --> 00:08:48,710
