89
00:08:55,710 --> 00:08:58,760
My son, Ruoxu, is young and ignorant.

90
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:03,230
Please take care of him in the future

91
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,280
and protect him to grow up.

92
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:07,960
Why do you

93
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,520
make such a request to me?

94
00:09:11,710 --> 00:09:12,440
Miss Zhu,

95
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:15,550
I have my reason.

96
00:09:15,550 --> 00:09:16,590
Please don't ask.

97
00:09:17,470 --> 00:09:18,030
Farewell.

98
00:09:58,400 --> 00:09:59,230
Black bees!

99
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:16,440
Bei Di…

100
00:10:17,790 --> 00:10:19,350
Bei Di killed somebody.

101
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:45,110
Xu…

102
00:10:46,710 --> 00:10:47,670
Ruoxu…

103
00:10:53,550 --> 00:10:54,400
Official Xu!

104
00:10:54,670 --> 00:10:55,280
Somebody was killed.

105
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,350
Somebody was killed on the street.

106
00:10:59,000 --> 00:10:59,790
He is Official Xu, isn't he?

107
00:11:03,550 --> 00:11:04,640
This is Official Xu.

108
00:11:04,670 --> 00:11:06,030
A spy of Bei Di has killed a man.

109
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:07,910
Official Xu is a good man.

110
00:11:07,910 --> 00:11:08,440
Yeah.

111
00:11:09,030 --> 00:11:10,470
The spy is so bad.

112
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:15,080
Stop!

113
00:11:17,350 --> 00:11:17,760
How dare you run!

114
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,150
How dare you!

115
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,440
How dare you!

116
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:20,840
Hit him.

117
00:11:21,030 --> 00:11:22,200
You killed creatures cruelly.

118
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:22,910
Even if you beat me to death,

119
00:11:22,910 --> 00:11:23,960
I'm not going to leave it alone.

120
00:11:30,110 --> 00:11:30,550
How dare you!

121
00:11:30,550 --> 00:11:31,320
Where are you going?

122
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:32,150
How dare you!

123
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,030
Hit him.

124
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:52,470
A monster!

125
00:11:52,470 --> 00:11:53,200
There is a monster.

126
00:11:53,590 --> 00:11:54,520
Come on, run!

127
00:11:55,470 --> 00:11:56,320
There's a monster. Run.

128
00:11:56,520 --> 00:11:57,230
A monster!

129
00:11:57,710 --> 00:11:58,320
Run!

130
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:16,960
Xu Ruoxu?

131
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:18,960
Yes, I am.

132
00:12:19,790 --> 00:12:20,520
Who are you?

133
00:12:21,110 --> 00:12:22,280
How do you know my name?

134
00:12:23,710 --> 00:12:24,400
That's a beast.

135
00:12:25,670 --> 00:12:27,000
Heaven has the virtue of cherishing life.

136
00:12:27,230 --> 00:12:27,960
I can't watch its tail be pulled off,

137
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,350
but didn't do anything.

138
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:30,840
Besides,

139
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:31,760
because of it,

140
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:32,840
I fell out with my father

141
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,550
and ran out.

142
00:12:46,710 --> 00:12:47,280
What are you doing?

143
00:12:48,520 --> 00:12:49,230
It's not delicious.

144
00:12:50,320 --> 00:12:51,400
Of course not.

145
00:12:52,150 --> 00:12:52,910
Who are you?

146
00:12:53,520 --> 00:12:54,000
Ling.

147
00:12:59,400 --> 00:13:00,000
Where are you going?

148
00:13:01,710 --> 00:13:02,640
Back to the hive.

149
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:04,110
Hive?

150
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:06,230
What is it?

151
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:10,230
Return to the hive to recuperate

152
00:13:11,520 --> 00:13:13,880
and replace the body

153
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:16,080
and then I can have

154
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:19,880
countless eyes and wings again.

155
00:13:20,880 --> 00:13:21,960
What are you talking about?

156
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:23,590
I can't understand at all.

157
00:13:29,350 --> 00:13:30,640
That's a strange man.

158
00:13:31,670 --> 00:13:32,640
I haven't seen what was going on.

159
00:13:32,640 --> 00:13:33,460
Official Xu actually fell.

160
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:33,820
There was a man in white

161
00:13:33,880 --> 00:13:34,840
who rushed here

162
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:36,840
and killed him.

163
00:13:37,520 --> 00:13:38,550
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

164
00:13:38,550 --> 00:13:39,150
He's right.

165
00:13:39,150 --> 00:13:40,030
Official Xu is a good man.

166
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:42,440
Mr. Lu,

167
00:13:42,590 --> 00:13:44,000
I have made clear who is the killer.

168
00:13:44,150 --> 00:13:45,200
It was a Bei Di boy.

169
00:13:45,790 --> 00:13:46,880
A Bei Di boy?

170
00:13:49,030 --> 00:13:50,840
How could a Bei Di boy have wings

171
00:13:51,230 --> 00:13:53,080
and fly away in full view?

172
00:13:53,400 --> 00:13:54,200
You are right.

173
00:13:54,760 --> 00:13:55,880
The killer was a beast

174
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:57,550
who disguised as a Bei Di boy.

175
00:14:00,230 --> 00:14:01,470
Were you with Official Xu all the time

176
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:03,670
before going back to the Inspection Department?

177
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:04,550
Yes, I was.

178
00:14:04,880 --> 00:14:06,150
I have been checking with Official Xu

179
00:14:06,150 --> 00:14:07,400
outside the cottage.

180
00:14:08,520 --> 00:14:09,350
What did you see?

181
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:11,840
On that day, Official Xu entered the house alone.

182
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:14,400
He was pale when he came out

183
00:14:15,150 --> 00:14:16,230
and kept saying

184
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:17,790
it's terrible.

185
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:19,790
Hurry up.

186
00:14:57,790 --> 00:14:59,320
We're still a step late.

187
00:15:00,470 --> 00:15:02,280
I think they are the things

188
00:15:03,110 --> 00:15:04,000
that Official Xu saw in the cottage that day.

189
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:06,840
They used beasts to kill people

190
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:10,000
and burned them down.

191
00:15:11,640 --> 00:15:12,640
None survived.

192
00:15:15,350 --> 00:15:16,710
None survived.

193
00:15:17,790 --> 00:15:18,230
Who's there?

194
00:15:24,710 --> 00:15:25,550
Who are you?

195
00:15:26,280 --> 00:15:26,790
Drop your hand.

196
00:15:27,110 --> 00:15:28,030
Or I will shoot arrows.

197
00:15:33,110 --> 00:15:33,550
Ling.

198
00:15:35,590 --> 00:15:36,030
Who is that?

199
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:44,520
Run!

200
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:04,110
Don't hurt him.

201
00:16:05,150 --> 00:16:05,760
Who is he?

202
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,200
He is Xu Ruoxu,

203
00:16:07,790 --> 00:16:08,710
the son of Official Xu.

204
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:09,590
Let's chase them.

205
00:16:10,470 --> 00:16:11,320
The beast can fly.

206
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:13,230
We can't catch them up.

207
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:16,960
This is the beast

208
00:16:17,550 --> 00:16:18,550
that killed Official Xu.

209
00:16:19,670 --> 00:16:20,880
How could Official Xu have thought

210
00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:22,960
that his son

211
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:25,320
saved the bee that killed him?

212
00:16:25,820 --> 00:16:28,640
[Langya Prefecture]

213
00:16:28,640 --> 00:16:29,960
It's a flying beast.

214
00:16:30,710 --> 00:16:31,670
We can confirm

215
00:16:32,020 --> 00:16:34,280
that Official Xu was killed by him.

216
00:16:38,880 --> 00:16:39,710
Is the beast

217
00:16:40,640 --> 00:16:41,670
a black bee?

218
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:43,150
Exactly.

219
00:16:44,440 --> 00:16:45,280
In the “Records of Beasts in the Continent”

220
00:16:45,280 --> 00:16:46,350
written by Official Xu,

221
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,320
there is a description of it.

222
00:16:48,350 --> 00:16:49,910
While the bee is killing people,

223
00:16:50,280 --> 00:16:51,590
it will also get the victim's memories.

224
00:16:52,710 --> 00:16:53,960
But it's not very detailed.

225
00:16:54,350 --> 00:16:56,670
Because few people have ever seen it.

226
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,710
Prince Nan also mentioned it to me.

227
00:17:04,710 --> 00:17:06,070
Looks like Bei Di people

228
00:17:06,280 --> 00:17:07,560
have domesticated black bees

229
00:17:07,560 --> 00:17:09,310
into killers.

230
00:17:10,070 --> 00:17:10,950
At all costs,

231
00:17:10,950 --> 00:17:12,310
we must find the beekeeper.

232
00:17:13,640 --> 00:17:14,070
Got it.

233
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:14,590
Got it.

234
00:17:16,430 --> 00:17:17,160
I have one more thing

235
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:19,040
to report to you, Your Highness.

236
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:24,950
The one who saved the black bee

237
00:17:26,310 --> 00:17:28,350
was Xu Ruoxu, Official Xu's son.

238
00:17:35,230 --> 00:17:36,350
Why him?

239
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:38,680
I don't know why either.

240
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:40,190
And

241
00:17:40,430 --> 00:17:42,710
the coroner has examined Official Xu's body

242
00:17:43,280 --> 00:17:43,950
and found out

243
00:17:44,190 --> 00:17:45,680
there are three moles in his palm.

244
00:17:46,830 --> 00:17:47,680
He said

245
00:17:48,710 --> 00:17:51,190
the moles look like a tattoo.

246
00:17:58,680 --> 00:17:59,950
It seems that Official Xu

247
00:18:01,040 --> 00:18:02,160
is deliberately protecting

248
00:18:02,160 --> 00:18:03,880
the man with three moles in his palm.

249
00:18:05,110 --> 00:18:06,430
This person is the one who can destroy Bei Di

250
00:18:06,950 --> 00:18:08,710
after 10 years in the prophecy.

251
00:18:27,520 --> 00:18:28,830
I know you're hungry.

252
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:30,880
But I don't have any money now.

253
00:18:33,430 --> 00:18:34,710
When I go home and get money tomorrow,

254
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:36,190
I'll buy you the best.

255
00:18:40,560 --> 00:18:44,110
What does that mean by none survived?

256
00:18:44,950 --> 00:18:45,830
That means

257
00:18:46,800 --> 00:18:47,830
there is no one left.

258
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:48,680
It's all gone.

259
00:18:57,430 --> 00:18:58,160
What happened to you?

260
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:00,160
Why?

261
00:19:00,710 --> 00:19:01,560
What?

262
00:19:02,040 --> 00:19:02,710
Why did I save you?

263
00:19:03,110 --> 00:19:04,110
Because you saved me first.

264
00:19:04,800 --> 00:19:05,520
Said the saint,

265
00:19:05,710 --> 00:19:07,280
within the four seas, all men are brothers.

266
00:19:09,070 --> 00:19:10,160
Then we'll be brothers.

267
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:17,160
Brothers.

268
00:19:20,280 --> 00:19:20,710
Go.

269
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:26,640
[Zhu]

270
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:28,400
I've been busy entertaining Prince Nan these days.

271
00:19:28,830 --> 00:19:30,590
I had no time to visit you.

272
00:19:31,190 --> 00:19:32,310
Sorry for that.

273
00:19:34,190 --> 00:19:36,190
After all, Tianxiang Restaurant is not a hotel

274
00:19:36,280 --> 00:19:38,430
where people are free to come and go.

275
00:19:38,950 --> 00:19:39,950
Miss Zhu loves to be quiet.

276
00:19:39,950 --> 00:19:40,950
As soon as the curtains hang,

277
00:19:40,950 --> 00:19:42,520
we have had no guests for about ten days.

278
00:19:42,520 --> 00:19:44,160
Your Highness, you don't have to stand on ceremony.

279
00:19:45,280 --> 00:19:46,190
That being said,

280
00:19:46,190 --> 00:19:47,400
in my heart,

281
00:19:47,520 --> 00:19:48,800
I really miss you.

282
00:19:52,190 --> 00:19:52,710
So,

283
00:19:53,070 --> 00:19:54,280
I especially got a rare ingredient

284
00:19:54,280 --> 00:19:56,400
for you.

285
00:19:56,710 --> 00:19:57,830
Mingyan, here.

286
00:19:58,280 --> 00:19:58,880
There seems to be something good.

287
00:19:58,880 --> 00:19:59,350
Really?

288
00:19:59,590 --> 00:20:00,160
Let me see.

289
00:20:07,310 --> 00:20:09,560
It has a sweet taste.

290
00:20:12,110 --> 00:20:13,640
But the sweetness

291
00:20:13,950 --> 00:20:15,760
is mixed with a smoky taste.

292
00:20:17,590 --> 00:20:19,000
It's a fly in the ointment.

